  <div> <span style="color:#c0392b;"><u><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><b>REMEMBER TO SEND THE CORRESPONDING BROCHURE FOR THE DISINFECTION SERVICE YOUR AREA OFFERS.</b></span></span></u></span> 
  </div> 
  <div> <span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="color:#c0392b;"><u><span style="font-size: 20px;"><b>(PLEASE REMOVE ONE, BOTH SANI-DEFENSE AND SANI-PLUS ARE AUTOMATICALLY&nbsp;&nbsp;LOADED INTO THE TEMPLATE)</b></span></u></span><br /> <span style="font-size:16px;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},<br /> <br /> I can imagine this is a stressful time, balancing the needs of your business while maintaining a safe and healthy facility.<br /> <br /> COVID-19 has reshaped several common practices, including business operating procedures and hygiene practices. Many of the businesses I work with are now looking to add increased hygiene measures throughout their facility, to better protect the health of their customers and employees.<br /> <br /> When your workforce returns, they will want to know their facility has minimized their exposure to harmful viruses and bacteria. This can be challenging to do, as businesses typically have several shared spaces including kitchens, washrooms and work spaces. <b style="font-size: 16px;">Each space within your facility can be a breeding&nbsp;ground for bacteria, and it is estimated that viruses such as COVID-19 can live on surfaces for up to 72 hours</b>. This means commonly touched items such as<i style="font-size: 16px;"> keyboards, door handles and cash registers</i> can transfer bacteria and viruses through surface-to-person contact.<br /> <br /> To better combat the spread of bacteria and viruses in the workplace, the <b>World Health Organization has set forth a recommendation for businesses to regularly clean and disinfect their facility, including commonly touched items</b>. Citron Hygiene understands the need for proper hygiene measures in the workplace, which is why we are offering our <a href="https://www.citronhygiene.com/professional-disinfection-services/">professional disinfection services</a> </span></span> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">. On a predetermined basis, Citron Hygiene’s trained hygiene technician will thoroughly disinfect your office and fixtures using a<b> DIN approved chemical</b>.<br /> <br /> I understand how important it is to have peace of mind when having your employees return to work, which is why Citron Hygiene takes a comprehensive approach to our disinfection service. Citron’s certified technicians receive in-depth training on how to perform disinfection services safely and successfully while wearing the proper protective equipment.<br /> <br /> I would like to set up a call to further discuss our disinfection in your facility,<i> as we recently received exciting news about our DIN approved disinfectant that I would like to share with you</i>. I am free to discuss virtually at your earliest convenience; I am confident in Citron’s ability to increase hygiene measures in your facility.<br /> <br /> I look forward to hearing from you, please don't&nbsp;hesitate to reach out if you have any questions.<br /> <br /> Thank you,<br /> <br /> {{{Sender.Name}}}</span></span> 
   <br /> 
